casebody.data:
Hickok, Appellant, v. Thurber, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

March 17, 1892.) Appeal from city court, general term. Action by Cornelius C. Hickok against Horace K. Thurber.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

E. P. Schell, for appellant. H. Aplington, for respondent.

Ho opinion. Order appealed from affirmed, with costs, and judgment absolute for the defendant.
